cs.CV, cs.AR, cs.EM, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a hardware solution for mobile computer vision tasks based on Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses energy efficiency, which could fall under cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) or cs.EM (Energy). The paper uses transfer learning, which is a common technique in machine learning, and could be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
